creator: Sara Teasdale
description:
LibriVox recording of Helen of Troy and Other Poems by Sara Teasdale.
Read in English by Katie Rose; Ian King; Davo Faulkner; Maria Kasper; Sonia; Zee Martin; Newgatenovelist; Jude; Christie Crews; Eric Burns; Shakira Searle; Kenita; Philippa; Kristin Gjerløw; Leonard Wilson; Jacquelyn Bengfort; Phil Schempf; mbm0rxi
Sara Teasdale was an American poet, originally from Missouri, later attaching herself more to New York. Helen of Troy was one of her first great successes. This volume also contains the small drama On the Tower, which is recorded here with a full cast.
Cast List:
Narrator: Maria Kasper
Lady: mbm0rxi
Knight: Kristin Gjerløw
Page: Shakira Searle
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
